‚úâÔ∏è feedback.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Feedback</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="index.html">Beranda</a>
    <a href="biodata.html">Biodata</a>
    <a href="galeri.html">Galeri</a>
    <a href="jadwal.html">Jadwal</a>
    <a href="feedback.html" class="active">Feedback</a>
  </nav>

  <form class="feedback-form" action="#" method="post">
    <h2>Kirim Feedback</h2>
    <label>Nama:</label>
    <input type="text" name="nama" required>

    <label>Email:</label>
    <input type="email" name="email" required>

    <label>Pesan:</label>
    <textarea name="pesan" rows="5" required></textarea>

    <button type="submit">Kirim</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>

üé® style.css
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

/* --- Navigasi Flexbox --- */
.navbar {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  background: #004d40;
}
.navbar a {
  color: white;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.navbar a:hover, .navbar .active {
  background: #00695c;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

/* --- Biodata --- */
.biodata-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20px;
}
.foto-profil {
  width: 200px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.bio-info {
  border-left: 4px solid #00695c;
  padding-left: 15px;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/* --- Galeri Flexbox --- */
.galeri {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px;
}
.card {
  flex: 1 1 100%;
  background: #f0f0f0;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-align: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

/* --- Tabel --- */
.table-container {
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}
table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
  width: 100%;
}
th, td {
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* --- Form --- */
.feedback-form {
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 20px;
}
.feedback-form input, .feedback-form textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 8px;
  border: 1px solid #aaa;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

/* --- Media Query Tablet --- */
@media (min-width: 600px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .biodata-container {
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .galeri .card {
    flex: 1 1 48%;
  }
}

/* --- Media Query Desktop --- */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .galeri .card {
    flex: 1 1 23%;
  }
  .feedback-form {
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .feedback-form input {
    width: 48%;
  }
  .feedback-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
  }
}

‚úÖ Ceklis Akhir
Fitur	Sudah Ada
Struktur folder benar	‚úÖ
CSS eksternal di semua halaman	‚úÖ
Menu navigasi Flexbox + hover	‚úÖ
Galeri Flexbox responsif	‚úÖ
Biodata responsif (stack ‚Üí 2 kolom)	‚úÖ
Tabel rowspan/colspan + scroll mobile	‚úÖ
Form lengkap & validasi HTML dasar	‚úÖ


